text: Arthur Griez von Ronse (died 17 March 1921) was an Austrian fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:1921 deaths Category:Austrian male fencers Category:Austrian épée fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Austria Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
